        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Stridulatory files of Altihoratosphaga species (wing articulation to the right). A, Altihoratosphaga hanangensis sp. nov. (paratype). B, Altihoratosphaga nou (CH7091). C, Altihoratosphaga montivaga (CH6890). D, Altihoratosphaga nomima (Ruaha National Park). Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
